# Sync Job Registry and Tracker Store to Desktop

After any operation that modifies the Fuyao job registry or the experiment tracker store, push to huh.desktop.us.

## Job Registry

After registry mutations (add, remove, clear, protect, unprotect, sync, batch update):

```bash
scp ~/.cursor/tmp/fuyao_job_registry.json huh.desktop.us:~/software/Experiment-Tracker-/fuyao_job_registry.json
```

## Tracker Store

After tracker recordings (record-deploy, record-sweep, set-status, update-sweep-status):

```bash
rsync -az ~/.exp-tracker/{graph.json,index.json,events.jsonl} huh.desktop.us:~/.exp-tracker/
```

Both pushes are non-blocking. If SSH is unreachable, warn and continue.
